information: Our passion lies in the element of water. Our expertise as a manufacturer and service provider spans multiple product groups. A key pillar of our business is aquarium production – we specialise in custom creations made of plexiglas, acrylic and glass, as well as large-scale aquariums. As another string to our bow, we have developed our own filtering, measurement and lighting technologies. Our field service is an all-round service: Aquarium maintenance and care with the necessary technology. Another key production area for us is water features. Water features represent an important element of modern architecture, both indoors and outdoors. In particular, the water wall is hugely popular, whether made from corten steel, stainless steel, glass or acrylic. We can also make water columns and wall fountains to meet your specific brief. Our third area of expertise lies in fountains. Our range of high-quality fountains are made from specially selected materials.
